    <div class="list-text">
    <a
    class="hed-heading -excerpt"
    href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/06/03/biden-united-states-kleptocracy-power-sanctions/">
    <h3 class="hed">Biden Could End Kleptocracy’s Grip on the United States</h3>
</a>
<div class="dek-heading -excerpt">
    <p class="dek">A new administration can make the changes needed to break a rotten global system. </p>
